        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "I answer the phone."
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "I am going to answer the phone."
        },
        {
          "id": "c",
          "text": "I'll answer the phone."
        },
        {
          "id": "d",
          "text": "I will answer the phone."
        }
      ],
      "correct_answer": "c",
      "explanation": "Правильное использование 'will' для моментального решения, как в примере 'The phone is ringing. I'll answer it.'",
